3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with controlling the power allocation in a distributed system of femtocells. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper proposes a multi-agent Q-learning approach for power allocation in femtocell networks. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with optimizing the capacity of femtocell networks, which is related to information theory.
